cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Trix in academic work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Trix"
abstract: >-
  An embeddable stack-based scripting virtual machine written as a
  single-header C++23 library.  Provides cooperative concurrency
  (coroutines, pipelines, actors, Erlang/OTP-style supervision),
  logic programming (unification, backtracking, choice points),
  reactive cells (incremental computation), lazy sequences,
  transactional save/restore, and whole-VM snapshot/thaw.
authors:
